{"tid":579772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台妹為了女兒繼承上億遺產自認通姦 DNA唔駛驗","createTime":"2018-03-04T02:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T13:12:19.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"df6cead396e6f859a3042a82777084cb03c5db9b","tid":579772,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"《聯合報》報導，桃園一名邱姓婦人與陳姓地主偷情，7年前生下女兒。邱因顧慮陳仍有婚姻，陳也不願婚外情曝光，兩人決定女兒從母姓。<br />\n2年前陳男病故，留下價值上億元的多筆房地產及存款。邱婦為了爭取女兒的繼承權，不惜「自曝通姦」，雖成功爭到女兒繼承遺產的權利，卻也讓自己被判2個月徒刑、可易科罰金。<br />\n法院審理時，邱婦認為女兒的權益不能被犧牲；陳男元配則不承認丈夫在外有私生女。對此邱婦要求比對DNA，但陳家拒驗。<br />\n法官依《民事訴訟法》規定，以拒驗血緣處於不利，加上邱婦提出的照片、支票等證據，認定陳外遇生女，判親子關係存在。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180304/1307858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180304%2F1307858&d=sOENwHjyvEI3yH8occPVRk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ec1d3608\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180304%2F1307858&h=4cf84ebc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180304/1307858</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2083943e37addb72cc6ac38e37b97b623152812f","tid":579772,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:26:37.000Z","msg":"幾張相就當係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣咁撚多on9法例"},{"pid":"63f0f366bd4d482fec5f3c98fa5a0a4987df9431","tid":579772,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2083943e37addb72cc6ac38e37b97b623152812f","tid":579772,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:26:37.000Z","msg":"幾張相就當係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣咁撚多on9法例"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:29:23.000Z","msg":"同郭台銘同照多幾張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae85a5e64039466faa766a0e5b971d948e197ed","tid":579772,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：台灣法律"},{"pid":"47dc9d2c5745e95827fe81bacecbc4ff231b599a","tid":579772,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cae85a5e64039466faa766a0e5b971d948e197ed","tid":579772,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：台灣法律"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"其實係咪近似民國初年既法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69749b2309e8126f2a1a8320f6bdec270e093854","tid":579772,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:05:09.000Z","msg":"點解陳家拒驗dna,驗左唔係親子關係咪唔使分俾佢<br />\n而家唔驗都係要俾佢地"},{"pid":"fedb31283b8e59981085927d883d39dbed2d9afb","tid":579772,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"所"},{"pid":"096e03f7a5322e7d8e592db32a12b6b9247e0c81","tid":579772,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69749b2309e8126f2a1a8320f6bdec270e093854","tid":579772,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:05:09.000Z","msg":"點解陳家拒驗dna,驗左唔係親子關係咪唔使分俾佢<br />\n而家唔驗都係要俾佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:12:19.000Z","msg":"私底下實比左報告佢睇啦"}]}